<title>New Ascent</title>

<div class="container">
  <header><img src="https://www.ft.com/__origami/service/image/v2/images/raw/http%3A%2F%2Fcom.ft.imagepublish.prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fe0e36980-6889-11e5-97d0-1456a776a4f5?fit=scale-down&amp;source=next&amp;width=700
  " width="300" height=200 class="img-responsive main-image"></header>
  <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">

  
    <h2>Add an Ascent</h2>

    <p>Here should be inputs for datetime and route. User = current_user, Peak = dropdown choice.<p>

    
<form action="/ascents" method="post">
  <p><label for="route">Route:</label>
  <input type="text" name="route"></p>
  <p><label for="date">Datetime:</label>
  <input type="text" name="date"></p>
  <select name="peak_id">
          <% @peaks.each.with_index(1) do |peak, i| %>
          <option value="<%= peak.id %>"><%= peak.name %></option>
  <% end %></select>
  <input type="submit" value="Submit"></form>

  <p><a href="/">Home</a>
  <p><form action="/logout" method="Post">		
      <input type="submit" value="Logout">	
  </form></p>